<h1 align="center"> Why we built Konverge </h1></div>
<p align="center"> We started this project after realizing our struggles to build meaningful relationships with other Kellogg students in a <b>consistent</b>, <b>scalable</b>, and <b>natural</b> way. Kellogg provides myriad opportunities (KWEST, sections, clubs) to bond with each other to form groups. Great, but... these groups also create barriers, whether real or perceived, that seem to hamper cross pollination and relationship building at the individual level. We built Konverge to create a more comfortable way to meet students. Our mission is to make Kellogg a stronger, long-term community. </p>
 
 

